    {
      "title": "Apply the quadratic formula",
      "content": "Here, $a=1$, $b=11$, and $c=8$.<br/>$$x=\\frac{-11\\pm\\sqrt{11^2-4(1)(8)}}{2(1)}$$<br/>$$x=\\frac{-11\\pm\\sqrt{89}}{2}$$<br/>The answer is <strong>A</strong>."
